channel.title: VPS Question
channel.description:
okay so my old VPS canceled there game package so i now have to look for some new ones...My old VPS was only 13.00 a month and could hold about 40 people. I have found a service called VPSLand and there prices are about the same. Could someone please tell me how many players i could hold with these stats:
[b]Processor: 0.5GHZ RAM: 512mb Storage: 10GB Bandwidth: 125GB[/b]
All i need to hold is about 40-50 people for now. Btw im using CentOS Linux VPS. thanks.
